Package: uzdoom
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Enhanced DOOM Source Port
 UZDoom is a modern, feature-rich source port for the classic game DOOM.
 .
 A continuation of ZDoom and GZDoom, UZDoom enhances the original DOOM
 engine, providing advanced features like:
 .
  * High-Resolution Graphics
  * Dynamic lighting
  * 3D Floors
  * Extensive Modding Support
  * Support for modern OpenGL and Vulkan renderers
 .
 UZDoom is free and open-source software, built and maintained by a
 dedicated community of developers and enthusiasts.
 .
 Note: You need a DOOM IWAD file (doom.wad, doom2.wad, etc.) to play.
